{
  "text": "The stability of the wide-angle transparent boundary conditions can be verified through a natural extension of our earlier analysis for the Schrödinger-type Padé-(2,0) approximant [CITATION_1] . Assume that the algorithm is implemented with exact arithmetic, and consider the representation of the exterior solution given by (14), namely",
